lemma PPs_closed_gcs: assumes "s \<in> .[X]" shows "gcs s t \<in> .[X]"
proof -
have "gcs s t adds s"
by (rule gcs_adds)
with assms(1)
show?thesis
by (rule PPs_closed_adds)
qed \<comment> \<open>We show that no integer polynomial crosses in $\<^const t$ over. To do the intelligent ideas, we present the case of $t$, in $\t\ (\in\in\Var t)$.\<close>
